
    VICTIMS of recent storms in Gauteng are still in need of help,
humanitarian organisation Gift of the Givers said today."The destruction…has been extensive, affecting
hundreds of homes spread out in a vast area. The houses include formal and
informal dwellings, with destruction of infrastructure, furniture, equipment,
clothing, food and, in some cases, vehicles, " the organisation said in a
statement.Even though Gift of the Givers was closed for the
